2. Under "subs", you'll find a list of objects denoted by "-" (hyphen). The objects can contain different properties such as id, Y, subs, etc.
3. The first object is the one that immediately follows the "subs". In this case, it is the object that has the id "f".
4. Therefore, the id of the first object of subs is "f".
